              <a href="https://wa.me/212710492846?text=Bonjour%20ChicAhmed%2C%20je%20souhaite%20commander%20le%20Smoking." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-product-wa"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M.057 24l1.687-6.163c-1.041-1.804-1.588-3.849-1.587-5.946.003-6.556 5.338-11.891 11.893-11.891 3.181.001 6.167 1.24 8.413 3.488 2.245 2.248 3.481 5.236 3.48 8.414-.003 6.557-5.338 11.892-11.893 11.892-1.99-.001-3.951-.5-5.688-1.448l-6.305 1.654z"/></svg>WhatsApp</a>
